OL,3,CEx-police officer convicted over death
OL,4,Cthreat 'lie' which led to man's arrest
OL,6,FA former police officer who falsely
OL,7,Fclaimed he had been issued with a
OL,8,Fdeath threat whilst working as a
OL,9,Fconstable in the PSNI was handed a
OL,10,Fsuspended sentence on Friday.
OL,12,FCraig Ronald Moffitt, whose address
OL,13,Fwas given as 'PSNI Mahon Road,
OL,14,FPortadown' appeared at Belfast Crown
OL,15,FCourt.
OL,17,FHe was handed a 16-month sentence,
OL,18,Fwhich was suspended for three years,
OL,19,Fby Judge Brian Sherrard who branded
OL,20,Fthe incident as "a stupid error."
