OL,3,CEx-police officer convicted over death
OL,4,Cthreat 'lie' which led to man's arrest
OL,6,FThe 37-year old pleaded guilty to
OL,7,Fperverting the course of justice on a
OL,8,Fdate between December 29, 2019 and
OL,9,FJanuary 3, 2020 - namely he falsely
OL,10,Falleged that a female informed him
OL,11,Fthat a male had arranged to have him
OL,12,F'done in.'
OL,14,FThe court heard that whilst working as
OL,15,Fa constable in the PSNI, Moffitt
OL,16,Ffalsely claimed to police colleagues
OL,17,Fthat he had been approached by the
OL,18,Fgirlfriend of an 'identified
OL,19,Findividual'.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/10
