OL,3,CEx-police officer convicted over death
OL,4,Cthreat 'lie' which led to man's arrest
OL,6,FMoffitt claimed that the woman told
OL,7,Fhim the 'identified individual' - who
OL,8,Fwas her boyfriend - had arranged to
OL,9,Fhave him killed and an intelligence
OL,10,Freport was lodged.
OL,12,FBranding this claim as a "lie", Judge
OL,13,FSherrard revealed that on January 2,
OL,14,F2020 Moffitt "doubled down on that
OL,15,Flie" by falsely reporting in a 999
OL,16,Fcall that a man has appeared at his
OL,17,Fhome armed with a gun and tried to
OL,18,Fshoot him.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/10
