OL,3,CEx-police officer convicted over death
OL,4,Cthreat 'lie' which led to man's arrest
OL,6,FDue to Moffitt's allegations, the man
OL,7,Fhe named was arrested, his home was
OL,8,Fsearched and his girlfriend was
OL,9,Finterviewed.
OL,11,FWhen it transpired Moffitt's claims
OL,12,Fwere false, he was interviewed in
OL,13,FFebruary 2020.
OL,15,FAt this stage, Moffitt maintained the
OL,16,Ffalse account - but later admitted the
OL,17,Fcharge of perverting the course of
OL,18,Fjustice.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/10
