OL,6,FAs a result, Moffitt left his job in
OL,7,Fthe PSNI and is now employed in the
OL,8,Fhospitality sector.
OL,10,FDuring Friday's sentencing it emerged
OL,11,Fthat Moffitt knew the 'identified
OL,12,Findividual' from a previous
OL,13,Finvestigation.
OL,15,FA defence barrister branded his
OL,16,Fclient's offending as "bizarre" and
OL,17,F"an attempt by a troubled man to
OL,18,Fobtain sympathy."
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G5/10
