OL,4,Cthreat 'lie' which led to man's arrest
OL,6,FThe barrister also spoke of a decline
OL,7,Fin Moffitt's mental health in the lead-
OL,8,Fup to his offending which resulted in
OL,9,Fhim being detained for a period.
OL,11,FSaying Moffitt has been "punished
OL,12,Falready" due to losing his job and his
OL,13,Fself-respect, the barrister spoke of
OL,14,Fhis client's previous good standing
OL,15,Fand the fact that he has "completely
OL,16,Fchanged his life".
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G6/10
