OL,6,FThe PSNI acknowledged the sentence
OL,7,Fhanded down and in a statement Chief
OL,8,FSuperintendent Stephen Wright, Head of
OL,9,FPolice Service Professional Standards
OL,10,FDepartment (PSD) said: "Once his
OL,11,Foffending came to light, Moffitt was
OL,12,Frightly dismissed by the Police
OL,13,FService in June 2021 following an
OL,14,Finvestigation by PSD, which ran
OL,15,Falongside the criminal investigation.
OL,17,F"The Police Service and the public
OL,18,Fdemand the highest standards of police
OL,19,Fofficers and staff, and the actions of
OL,20,FMoffitt stand in stark contrast to
OL,21,Fthose standards.
